*gliv-1.6 (17 Oct 2002)

  17 Oct 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> :

  Update version.

*gliv-1.5.3 (28 Jun 2002)

  28 Jun 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> gliv-1.5.3.ebuild :

  New version.  Resolves bug #4096 thanks to quick responce from the
  author/maintainer of gliv :)

*gliv-1.5.2 (20 Jun 2002)

  20 Jun 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> gliv-1.5.2.ebuild :
  New version; update for >=gtkglarea-1.99.0.

  20 Jun 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> gliv-1.5.1.ebuild :
  Do some gnome2 cleanups.  For instance, we have to use the old gtk+-1.2
  while gliv do not support >=gtkglarea-1.99.0.

*gliv-1.5.1 (21 March 2002)

*gliv-1.5 (6 March 2002)

*gliv-1.4.5 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
